Usage: set_max_time_borrow [-help] <borrow_value> <object_list> [-interface]

-help                     # Prints out the command usage
<borrow_value>            # Max time borrow value (float, required)
<object_list>             # List of objects: pins, instances or clocks
                          # (string, required)
-interface                # Specifies for IO paths (bool, optional)